ent-CMPosterTartarus-name = Tartarus Mining co. poster
ent-CMPosterTartarus-desc = A simplified version of the Tartarus Mining co. logo. The Tartarus Mining Company is owned by Prospectia, a sub-division of the San Rei Corporation, which is in turn owned by the Weston-Yamada Corporation.

ent-CMPosterEATBlue-name = EAT
ent-CMPosterEATBlue-desc = This is less of a poster and more of an advertisement for those gross power bars.

ent-CMPosterCola-name = classic cola poster
ent-CMPosterCola-desc = This poster depicts a classic cola can. With a taste that's been around for centuries. Nobody can beat it.

