ent-RMCPosterWEYA1-name = Weston-Yamada poster
ent-RMCPosterWEYA1-desc = A Weston-Yamada logo featuring a stylized wireframe planet and the company slogan: The Future is Now.

ent-RMCPosterWEYA2-name = Weston-Yamada poster
ent-RMCPosterWEYA2-desc = You don't have much choice in brand loyalty when there's basically only one brand.

