ent-RMCPosterWEYA4-name = Weston-Yamada propaganda poster
ent-RMCPosterWEYA4-desc = TOGETHER - EXTRASOLAR COLONIZATION - WEAPON - PROTECTION - HIGH TECHNOLOGY - MANUFACTURING SYNTHETICS - FUTURE - SPACE STATION. Weston-Yamada - The Future is Now.

ent-RMCPosterWEYA5-name = Weston-Yamada propaganda poster
ent-RMCPosterWEYA5-desc = LET'S WORK - TOGETHER WE BUILD A BETTER FUTURE.

ent-CMPosterDaniel1-name = Synthetic 'Daniel' poster
ent-CMPosterDaniel1-desc = An ominous forward facing profile of the Synthetic model 'Daniel'. Not quite a second generation model but something inbetween, suited for the needs of colonists. The poster is more art then an advertisement.

ent-CMPosterDaniel2-name = Synthetic 'Daniel' poster
ent-CMPosterDaniel2-desc = An ominous side facing profile of the Synthetic model 'Daniel'. Not quite a second generation model but something inbetween, suited for the needs of colonists. The poster is more art then an advertisement.

ent-CMPosterDaniel3-name = Weston-Yamada - 'Daniel' Model Synthetic poster
ent-CMPosterDaniel3-desc = A poster depicting a child in the arms of a Weston-Yamada 'Daniel' model Synthetic, Who thought this was a good idea?

ent-CMPosterDaniel4-name = Synthetic 'Daniel' poster
ent-CMPosterDaniel4-desc = An ominous forward facing profile of the Synthetic model 'Daniel'. Not quite a second generation model but something inbetween, suited for the needs of colonists. The poster is more art then an advertisement.

