ent-CMPosterDaniel6-desc = A poster depicting a child in the arms of a Weston-Yamada 'Daniel' model Synthetic, Who thought this was a good idea?

ent-CMPosterDaniel7-name = Weston-Yamada - 'Daniel' Model Synthetic poster
ent-CMPosterDaniel7-desc = All that matters is YOUR comfort. Our Artificial Humans are watching your back.

ent-CMPosterMarineCorp1-name = marine corp poster
ent-CMPosterMarineCorp1-desc = Join the Marine Corp. Enlist today, protect tomorrow!

ent-CMPosterMarineCorp2-name = marine corp poster
ent-CMPosterMarineCorp2-desc = Join the Marine Corp. Enlist today, protect tomorrow!

ent-CMPosterMarineCorp3-name = marine corp poster
ent-CMPosterMarineCorp3-desc = Every Paycheck a Fortune! Every Formation a Parade! - Join the Colonial Marines!

ent-CMPosterMarineCorp4-name = marine corp poster
ent-CMPosterMarineCorp4-desc = This poster depicts the logo of the UN Marine Corps, Oorah!

ent-CMPosterMarineCorp5-name = UN marine corp poster
ent-CMPosterMarineCorp5-desc = YOU GIVE US WINGS, WINGS OF LIBERTY - United Nations Marine Corp.

ent-CMPosterMarineCorp6-name = UN marine corp poster
ent-CMPosterMarineCorp6-desc = UNMC MARINES - FIRST TO FIGHT.

ent-CMPosterMarineCorp7-name = UN marine corp poster
ent-CMPosterMarineCorp7-desc = No one stands alone with the United Nations Marine Corp - JOIN US!

ent-CMPosterFORECON-name = UN marine corp poster
ent-CMPosterFORECON-desc = Join the elite 'Recon Division of the United Nations Marine Corps', and become the unseen force that strikes fear into the hearts of our enemies. Harness your instinct, adaptability, and unwavering focus as you navigate hostile territories on distant planets.

ent-RMCPosterTSEPA1-name = TSEPA poster
ent-RMCPosterTSEPA1-desc = A recruitment poster for the TSEPA. Integrity, Justice, Unity. Together, We Keep the Peace.

ent-RMCPosterTSEPA2-name = TSEPA poster
ent-RMCPosterTSEPA2-desc = A recruitment poster for the TSEPA. Serve with Honor, Protect with Strength.

ent-RMCPosterTSEPA3-name = TSEPA poster
ent-RMCPosterTSEPA3-desc = A recruitment poster for the TSEPA. One Law, One Duty, One Force. Join the TSEPA.

ent-CMPosterSPP1-name = The Stars Are Ours
ent-CMPosterSPP1-desc = A giant man wearing an EVA suit holds fast with a waving flag of the SPP.

ent-CMPosterSPP2-name = The Stars Are Ours
ent-CMPosterSPP2-desc = A stylized depiction of the SPP home system and the stars

ent-CMPosterSPP3-name = Trust In The Strength Of The Union
ent-CMPosterSPP3-desc = A stylized depiction of the SPP star.

ent-CMPosterSPP4-name = Through The Union Our Power Is Secured
ent-CMPosterSPP4-desc = A stylized depiction of the SPP's flag and the words, 'Our Unity is the dream of all Peoples. Trust in the strength of their Union.'

ent-CMPosterSPP5-name = We Forge A Path Into the Stars
ent-CMPosterSPP5-desc = The head of a man in a SPPAC EVA suit smiles looking not at you, but up to the right of the poster.

ent-CMPosterSPP6-name = Our Militaries Secures Our Future
ent-CMPosterSPP6-desc = A SPPAC Ground Forces soldier stands, rifle at the ready with a defiant and steel-eyed look on his face. The SPP star is in the background.

ent-CMPosterSPP7-name = The People's Armed Collective Is Our Backbone
ent-CMPosterSPP7-desc = SPPAC Ground Forces soldiers, one of whom is a woman and none of whom have a clear race, stare forward stoically.

ent-CMPosterSPP8-name = The People's Armed Collective Is Our Backbone
ent-CMPosterSPP8-desc = SPPAC Ground Forces soldiers, one of whom is a woman and none of whom have a clear race, stare forward stoically. The poster reads, 'The People's Armed Collective represent us all in the sacred war of liberation and defense of the People's Union.

ent-CMPosterSPP9-name = Ever Vigilant Against Capitalist Forces
ent-CMPosterSPP9-desc = A warped screaming eagle made to look like a vulture bears its talons over the SPP homeworld which has the SPP roundel super-imposed over it. The poster reads, 'The UN will not break the resolve of the people.'

ent-CMPosterSPP10-name = Ever Vigilant Against The Stooges of Capitalism and Imperialism
ent-CMPosterSPP10-desc = A decrepit and desiccated, near claw-like hand reaches towards a stylized solar star shaped into the SPP star. The poster reads, 'Even in its death throes, we must remain vigilant of the encroachment of capitalist forces.'

